296
0:12:07.735,000 --> 0:12:08,000
This brutal pragmatism that she had,

297
0:12:09.312,000 --> 0:12:1,000
I mean, I was four and she told me,

298
0:12:11.106,000 --> 0:12:13,000
"Mommy is Santa." (Laughter)

299
0:12:13.429,000 --> 0:12:15,000
She was this brutal pragmatism.

300
0:12:15.912,000 --> 0:12:17,000
She taught me so many lessons,

301
0:12:18.285,000 --> 0:12:19,000
but the most important lesson

302
0:12:20.118,000 --> 0:12:23,000
