306
0:12:32.643,000 --> 0:12:33,000
and because of those words,

307
0:12:34.459,000 --> 0:12:37,000
I would love school more than anything,

308
0:12:37.471,000 --> 0:12:38,000
and because of those words, when I was on a bus

309
0:12:39.404,000 --> 0:12:42,000
going to school, I dreamed the biggest dreams.

310
0:12:42.657,000 --> 0:12:45,000
And it's because of those words that I stand here right now

311
0:12:45.76,000 --> 0:12:46,000
full of passion,

312
0:12:47.716,000 --> 0:12:49,000
asking you to be brave for the kids

313
0:12:50.124,000 --> 0:12:52,000
