0:13:19.43,000 --> 0:13:2,000
You see this idea of being the land

325
0:13:21.368,000 --> 0:13:22,000
of the free and the home of the brave,

326
0:13:23.042,000 --> 0:13:26,000
it's woven into the fabric of America.

