335
0:13:44.512,000 --> 0:13:48,000
As citizens, I'm asking you not to leave any child behind.

336
0:13:48.552,000 --> 0:13:5,000
I'm asking you not to be color blind,

337
0:13:51.007,000 --> 0:13:53,000
